Version 1.0beta2 - released 2014-10-07
* fixed several flaws and minor bugs
* lifted requirements to CMSimple_XH >= 1.6 and PHP >= 5.1.2
* added CSRF protection
* added support for XH 1.6 APIs
* added possibility to edit existing posts
* added strikethrough button to editor
* added Danish translation (contributed by maeg)
* added German translation
* added German manual
* added version.nfo
* removed powered-by link
* updated markItUp! to 1.1.14
* updated data/.htaccess for Apache 2.4
* refactored

Version 1beta1 - released 2012-06-09
* initial release
